OL,3,CStudent who was allegedly murdered
OL,4,Cdied on her birthday, an inquest heard
OL,6,FA university student who was allegedly
OL,7,Fmurdered in her halls of residence
OL,8,Fdied on her birthday, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FCarla-Maria Georgescu was found in her
OL,12,Froom in Victoria Street, Preston, at
OL,13,Fthe University of Lancashire, on 4
OL,14,FFebruary.
OL,16,FHer death was confirmed on her 20th
OL,17,Fbirthday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
