OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772062285
OL,3,CStudent who was allegedly murdered
OL,4,Cdied on her birthday, an inquest heard
OL,6,FNathan Owens, 34, of Hopps Street,
OL,7,FHartlepool, has been charged with her
OL,8,Fmurder alongside intentional
OL,9,Fstrangulation and Section 18 grieving
OL,10,Fbodily harm.
OL,12,FHe has been remanded in custody to
OL,13,Fappear at Preston Crown Court for a
OL,14,Fplea and trial hearing in April.
OL,16,FCarla-Maria was born in Bucharest in
OL,17,FRomania and was a full-time clinical
OL,18,Fpsychologist and second-year student,
OL,19,Fthe court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
