OL,3,CStudent who was allegedly murdered
OL,4,Cdied on her birthday, an inquest heard
OL,6,FArea Coroner Emma Mather said: "I am
OL,7,Ftold that Miss Georgescu's body was
OL,8,Fidentified by way of her passport and
OL,9,FID card."
OL,11,FThe inquest was adjourned to allow the
OL,12,Fcriminal proceedings to continue.
